{"tid":1223462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以幫手整理05年韓農反世貿騷亂","createTime":"2019-06-14T17:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T17:15:58.000Z","uid":249721,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45cb6d6beb4a99039d5a298f12250fc69c3545f6","tid":1223462,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"警察過份使用武力呢幾日已經鋪天蓋地，好想乘勝追擊，唔好比佢停！！！要還所有受傷嘅義士一個公道！<br />\n我打算用05年WTO單實際例子做比較<br />\n<br />\n反世貿From wiki : 34枚催淚彈和6顆布袋彈<br />\n警察受傷人數 : 61<br />\n612 : 150枚催淚彈、20發布袋彈、數枚橡膠子彈，其中施放的催淚彈較2014年佔中時施放87枚催淚彈多出逾7成。<br />\n警察受傷人數 : 22<br />\n05年嗰單全部成年人，騷亂程度遠超612，612絕大部分係學生但衝擊2野就比警察當狗咁追住黎打。<br />\n<br />\n我想呢2日周街派，請大家幫手一齊整理或者有冇其他提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d937509e1328feee8e585d9a41036631c352d48b","tid":1223462,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:09:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22074dd3de0ab091d9b78a99ea08541542fdac55","tid":1223462,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda5dc27bc992675816735cf7d178141535678be","tid":1223462,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2730bafd0bbf54c5bec82df7f570cb02a11cb4a6","tid":1223462,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:10:22.000Z","msg":"push！"},{"pid":"a50798914792ca86340e4b9bd04da9e54edeb108","tid":1223462,"uid":1303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:10:37.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻少少時間，希望可以入黎睇睇！<br />\n<br />\n抗爭之後，有更重要既事我地要去做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.k